		<title>寵物也可能有「社交焦慮」？一次看懂5招超有效安撫技巧！</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/09/%e5%af%b5%e7%89%a9%e4%b9%9f%e5%8f%af%e8%83%bd%e6%9c%89%e3%80%8c%e7%a4%be%e4%ba%a4%e7%84%a6%e6%85%ae%e3%80%8d%ef%bc%9f%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e7%9c%8b%e6%87%825%e6%8b%9b%e8%b6%85%e6%9c%89%e6%95%88%e5%ae%89/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 09 Aug 2025 07:34:43 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
